videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr.  drives and passes to Rodney Miller Jr. who jams it home for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Good passing by Miami leads to Miller dunk

videos.description: Dewan Huell gets pass the defender to make the tough shot plus the foul.
videos.headline: Miami's Huell spins to make and-1 shot

videos.description: Edward Simpson drives and scores just to beat the 1st-half buzzer.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee's Simpson scores layup at buzzer

videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr. uses crossover dribble to create space allowing him to hit the shot plus a foul.
videos.headline: Miami's Brown Jr. makes and-1 floater

videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr. works his way around several defenders to score a up-and-under layup.
videos.headline: Miami's Brown Jr. dribbles through the defense to score

videos.description: Blue Raiders force a turnover as Antwain Johnson passes to Nick King who jams it home on the other end.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee turns steal into King dunk

videos.description: Anthony Lawrence II inbounds the ball to Bruce Brown Jr. who scores the basket plus a foul to seal win for Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Miami throws long inbound pass for Brown Jr. and-1 layup
